00:00:11,669 --> 00:00:21,664
♪In ancient times, a meteor fell♪

2
00:00:22,528 --> 00:00:29,920
♪Scorching Nanba Weald into land bare♪

3
00:00:30,336 --> 00:00:39,993
♪From Turquoise Land beneath the sun♪

4
00:00:41,088 --> 00:00:52,256
♪The evil Earth Fiends were born♪

5
00:00:55,168 --> 00:00:58,400
♪Marching in South Mountain's domain♪

6
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,248
♪Sworn warriors raged for glory's gain♪

7
00:01:01,248 --> 00:01:03,328
♪Renamed guardians hold Yanguan true♪

8
00:01:03,328 --> 00:01:06,656
♪Peace in all lands, a priceless boon♪

9
00:01:12,224 --> 00:01:15,264
♪Seven hounds, two whips, one blade♪

10
00:01:15,264 --> 00:01:18,048
♪In rout and flight,
Earth Fiends escape♪

11
00:01:18,048 --> 00:01:20,839
♪Golden Gate seals fast♪

12
00:01:20,872 --> 00:01:25,243
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

13
00:01:26,752 --> 00:01:37,024
♪South Mountain Hunters
on the righteous path♪

14
00:01:37,024 --> 00:01:41,216
=Love on the Turquoise Land=

15
00:01:41,216 --> 00:01:44,000
(This story is a work of fiction)

16
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,960
=Episode 5=

17
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:52,792
(Yan Tuo)

18
00:02:56,088 --> 00:02:59,828
(Yan Tuo, General Manager
of Roadsound Group)

19
00:03:02,072 --> 00:03:03,672
(Legal Representative, Lin Xirou)

20
00:03:06,584 --> 00:03:08,280
(Mr. Lu)

21
00:03:10,652 --> 00:03:12,611
Could you stop rushing me?

22
00:03:13,932 --> 00:03:15,092
The world has changed.

23
00:03:15,411 --> 00:03:17,372
Aesthetic tastes
are growing more unpredictable.

24
00:03:18,252 --> 00:03:19,411
What are you talking about?

25
00:03:20,252 --> 00:03:21,652
Your unmarketable new creation

26
00:03:21,691 --> 00:03:22,851
caught someone's eye.

27
00:03:23,332 --> 00:03:24,131
Really?

28
00:03:25,932 --> 00:03:26,812
I told him

29
00:03:27,131 --> 00:03:27,972
only drafts exist

30
00:03:27,972 --> 00:03:29,291
and the final product isn't done.

31
00:03:29,932 --> 00:03:30,652
Yet he insisted

32
00:03:30,972 --> 00:03:32,812
it's okay and he'd wait.

33
00:03:34,972 --> 00:03:36,212
Don't joke with me.

34
00:03:36,571 --> 00:03:37,652
Not sure if it's a joke.

35
00:03:38,052 --> 00:03:39,611
He prepaid for three pieces outright.

36
00:03:39,972 --> 00:03:40,772
He only wants

37
00:03:40,932 --> 00:03:41,972
to meet you

38
00:03:42,291 --> 00:03:43,372
and discuss art in person.

39
00:03:44,052 --> 00:03:44,972
Who is he?

40
00:03:45,332 --> 00:03:48,212
We can't pry about his background.

41
00:03:48,571 --> 00:03:50,212
Anyway, he's declared

42
00:03:50,652 --> 00:03:52,291
he'll buy whatever you produce.

43
00:03:52,972 --> 00:03:54,731
See? The world has changed.

44
00:04:20,652 --> 00:04:22,252
Are you sure nothing is wrong with him?

45
00:04:22,451 --> 00:04:23,851
A decent business owner.

46
00:04:24,372 --> 00:04:26,611
He started from scratch
through honest work.

47
00:04:26,812 --> 00:04:28,731
Since when do decent people
meet in cemeteries?

48
00:04:28,932 --> 00:04:30,492
It's why he's remarkable.

49
00:04:30,772 --> 00:04:31,451
Think about it.

50
00:04:31,652 --> 00:04:33,731
No invite to dinner
avoids dietary preferences.

51
00:04:33,932 --> 00:04:35,812
No invite to drinks
prevent seeming frivolous.

52
00:04:36,332 --> 00:04:38,972
No office meet avoids formal stiffness.

53
00:04:38,972 --> 00:04:39,812
No gallery meeting

54
00:04:39,851 --> 00:04:42,372
presumes you've outgrown such spaces.

55
00:04:42,492 --> 00:04:45,411
Which place has serene
yet meaningful setting

56
00:04:45,411 --> 00:04:46,812
suitable for discussing art freely

57
00:04:46,812 --> 00:04:48,372
and contemplating life deeply?

58
00:04:48,372 --> 00:04:49,851
Hotel executive lounge?

59
00:04:49,851 --> 00:04:50,731
Too pedestrian.

60
00:04:51,212 --> 00:04:52,372
Can a lounge allow you

61
00:04:52,372 --> 00:04:53,492
to explore life's essence,

62
00:04:53,891 --> 00:04:55,532
human destiny,

63
00:04:55,691 --> 00:04:57,812
or the end of life?

64
00:04:58,891 --> 00:04:59,812
I need to go.

65
00:05:00,171 --> 00:05:01,012
I see him.

66
00:05:07,772 --> 00:05:09,132
Is this how you treat clients?

67
00:05:10,572 --> 00:05:11,652
I'll require a refund.

68
00:05:11,931 --> 00:05:13,731
No need. I won't sell it to you.

69
00:05:13,931 --> 00:05:15,811
Your work is about rebirth, right?

70
00:05:18,572 --> 00:05:19,371
Madman.

71
00:05:24,692 --> 00:05:25,931
Though newly created

72
00:05:26,212 --> 00:05:27,291
with limited impact,

73
00:05:28,012 --> 00:05:29,251
I've read critiques

74
00:05:29,972 --> 00:05:31,291
that mostly interpret your work

75
00:05:31,611 --> 00:05:35,212
as depicting suffocation and confinement

76
00:05:36,051 --> 00:05:37,652
and conveying dark emotions.

77
00:05:39,692 --> 00:05:40,652
If you continue,

78
00:05:40,652 --> 00:05:42,332
you'll expose your ignorance.

79
00:05:46,491 --> 00:05:47,452
Whenever I come here,

80
00:05:48,132 --> 00:05:50,212
I don't feel death or fear.

81
00:05:51,491 --> 00:05:52,572
Your sculptures

82
00:05:52,652 --> 00:05:53,411
inexplicably

83
00:05:53,411 --> 00:05:54,611
don't oppress me.

84
00:05:55,291 --> 00:05:56,892
They evoke childbirth's struggle.

85
00:05:57,332 --> 00:05:59,692
Of course, it's agonizing

86
00:06:00,092 --> 00:06:01,371
for the mother and child,

87
00:06:02,171 --> 00:06:03,012
yet the miracle

88
00:06:03,012 --> 00:06:04,731
of new life emerging

89
00:06:05,132 --> 00:06:06,332
is the ultimate hope.

90
00:06:06,972 --> 00:06:07,491
So I believe

91
00:06:07,491 --> 00:06:08,772
you're fundamentally optimistic.

92
00:06:09,611 --> 00:06:11,452
True, I'm no art expert,

93
00:06:11,731 --> 00:06:12,772
but I'm not pretending.

94
00:06:12,892 --> 00:06:14,411
I genuinely admire your work.

95
00:06:18,772 --> 00:06:20,332
Let me share my interpretation.

96
00:06:20,332 --> 00:06:21,332
I'm all ears.

97
00:06:23,132 --> 00:06:24,332
Outsiders see

98
00:06:24,491 --> 00:06:25,811
a pampered heir

99
00:06:25,972 --> 00:06:27,371
living carefree.

100
00:06:27,772 --> 00:06:29,931
Even you've bought into this facade,

101
00:06:30,092 --> 00:06:30,731
trapped in

102
00:06:30,731 --> 00:06:32,892
an identity and fate you despise.

103
00:06:33,652 --> 00:06:35,452
If you truly appreciated my art,

104
00:06:36,092 --> 00:06:37,452
you'd recognize

105
00:06:37,491 --> 00:06:39,332
the dark emotions, such as suffocation

106
00:06:39,332 --> 00:06:40,452
and confinement

107
00:06:41,411 --> 00:06:42,851
that mirror your reality,

108
00:06:43,811 --> 00:06:44,972
instead of standing

109
00:06:45,132 --> 00:06:46,051
in front of me,

110
00:06:46,171 --> 00:06:47,772
spouting empty praise.

111
00:06:52,572 --> 00:06:54,051
Surprising depth of understanding

112
00:06:54,291 --> 00:06:55,851
for new acquaintances like us.

113
00:06:56,892 --> 00:06:59,452
I have no interest in understanding
a reckless madman

114
00:06:59,452 --> 00:07:00,931
who'd drown others with him in a car.

115
00:07:01,892 --> 00:07:03,452
My apologies. I acted rashly.

116
00:07:03,972 --> 00:07:05,772
I just wanted calm dialogue

117
00:07:05,772 --> 00:07:07,012
and honest communication.

118
00:07:07,411 --> 00:07:08,171
If you still think

119
00:07:08,171 --> 00:07:09,532
I'm mad after hearing me out,

120
00:07:10,491 --> 00:07:11,532
I'll put a stop to it.

121
00:07:11,532 --> 00:07:12,532
No more bothering.

122
00:07:20,772 --> 00:07:21,611
I'm not sure

123
00:07:21,611 --> 00:07:22,892
what you gain from being here.

124
00:07:23,772 --> 00:07:25,212
But this place makes me uneasy.

125
00:07:25,411 --> 00:07:26,132
Get to the point.

126
00:07:28,411 --> 00:07:31,332
I invited you here
to show you a piece of work.

127
00:07:33,212 --> 00:07:33,731
Work?

128
00:07:34,371 --> 00:07:35,012
A tombstone.

129
00:07:44,532 --> 00:07:45,411
A woman

130
00:07:46,611 --> 00:07:47,931
ruined my family.

131
00:07:49,012 --> 00:07:50,572
(Lin Xirou)
She even stole my mother's name.

132
00:07:51,572 --> 00:07:52,332
Lin Xirou is now

133
00:07:53,772 --> 00:07:55,652
in charge of the entire Roadsound Group,

134
00:07:55,652 --> 00:07:56,731
living carefree.

135
00:07:58,291 --> 00:08:01,012
This tombstone was erected for my mother

136
00:08:01,611 --> 00:08:02,972
and will also eventually be hers.

137
00:08:03,772 --> 00:08:06,291
Are you saying your biological mother
was named Lin Xirou,

138
00:08:07,092 --> 00:08:10,371
and the current Lin Xirou
of Roadsound Group

139
00:08:11,092 --> 00:08:12,491
is the one who killed her?

140
00:08:29,692 --> 00:08:30,892
I got you.

141
00:08:31,692 --> 00:08:32,411
Wait a bit longer.

142
00:08:32,532 --> 00:08:33,572
Dad will be home soon.

143
00:08:35,212 --> 00:08:35,811
Tuo.

144
00:08:36,371 --> 00:08:37,572
Dad.

145
00:08:38,291 --> 00:08:39,132
Sorry for being late.

146
00:08:39,371 --> 00:08:40,171
Here.

147
00:08:40,332 --> 00:08:42,371
Happy birthday.

148
00:08:42,371 --> 00:08:44,012
Such a beautiful toy car.

149
00:08:44,012 --> 00:08:44,972
Do you like it?

150
00:08:44,972 --> 00:08:46,851
Yes, I love it.

151
00:08:46,851 --> 00:08:49,051
Who is she?

152
00:08:50,692 --> 00:08:51,371
Honey,

153
00:08:52,532 --> 00:08:53,972
this is Li Ergou's sister,

154
00:08:54,132 --> 00:08:55,772
Shuangxiu. Li Shuangxiu.

155
00:08:57,332 --> 00:08:59,012
Since the baby you're carrying develops,

156
00:08:59,051 --> 00:09:00,772
and there's so much housework,

157
00:09:00,892 --> 00:09:02,731
Shuangxiu will stay here from now on.

158
00:09:02,851 --> 00:09:04,212
Order her around for chores

159
00:09:04,332 --> 00:09:05,892
like she's one of our family.

160
00:09:05,892 --> 00:09:07,532
Let me show you the place.

161
00:09:08,851 --> 00:09:11,171
You're about to give birth
and you're still doing chores.

162
00:09:11,171 --> 00:09:12,772
Dashan went to pick Tuo up from school.

163
00:09:12,931 --> 00:09:14,171
I'll go meet them halfway.

164
00:09:53,011 --> 00:09:53,731
Tuo,

165
00:09:55,812 --> 00:09:57,972
I have something very important to do.

166
00:09:59,011 --> 00:10:00,771
Be good and wait here, okay?

167
00:10:21,731 --> 00:10:25,131
Tuo, you may call me
Ms. Lin from now on.

168
00:10:25,812 --> 00:10:26,812
Ms. Lin.

169
00:10:32,491 --> 00:10:33,812
My full name is Lin Xirou.

170
00:10:48,851 --> 00:10:49,771
After that,

171
00:10:50,212 --> 00:10:51,251
she became

172
00:10:51,251 --> 00:10:52,692
the lady of our household.

173
00:10:55,812 --> 00:10:57,371
As a kid, I was clueless.

174
00:10:57,692 --> 00:10:58,771
For years,

175
00:10:58,771 --> 00:11:00,491
I had genuinely considered
her my family.

176
00:11:04,011 --> 00:11:05,371
After I eventually found

177
00:11:05,371 --> 00:11:06,651
my mother's diary,

178
00:11:06,771 --> 00:11:07,611
I realized...

179
00:11:12,212 --> 00:11:13,412
Why are you telling me this?

180
00:11:15,052 --> 00:11:15,972
Gou Ya

181
00:11:16,572 --> 00:11:18,452
was sent to the welfare home
by Lin Xirou.

182
00:11:19,692 --> 00:11:21,092
If he's truly an Earth Fiend,

183
00:11:22,251 --> 00:11:23,972
then Lin Xirou must control the key

184
00:11:24,052 --> 00:11:25,891
to transforming Earth Fiends
into human form.

185
00:11:27,292 --> 00:11:28,452
What else do you know?

186
00:11:28,812 --> 00:11:31,172
I've looked for a long time.
But she's too cautious.

187
00:11:32,292 --> 00:11:33,491
She has guarded against me.

188
00:11:34,292 --> 00:11:35,172
I found nothing.

189
00:11:35,812 --> 00:11:37,412
But now that Gou Ya is in trouble

190
00:11:37,932 --> 00:11:38,851
and I've met you

191
00:11:39,011 --> 00:11:40,172
and your organization,

192
00:11:40,771 --> 00:11:41,851
it gives me hope.

193
00:11:42,851 --> 00:11:43,972
I just want to know

194
00:11:43,972 --> 00:11:45,092
what I should do

195
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:47,092
(Lin Xirou)
to avenge my mother.

196
00:11:48,651 --> 00:11:50,011
First, you need to find out

197
00:11:50,212 --> 00:11:51,572
exactly what Lin Xirou is.

198
00:11:51,891 --> 00:11:53,131
I don't care what she is.

199
00:11:54,891 --> 00:11:56,292
But I'm certain

200
00:11:56,531 --> 00:11:58,292
her connection
to Earth Fiends is unusual.

201
00:11:59,651 --> 00:12:00,851
If you truly oppose

202
00:12:00,851 --> 00:12:01,731
the Earth Fiends,

203
00:12:02,011 --> 00:12:02,771
working with me

204
00:12:03,371 --> 00:12:04,731
is a golden opportunity.

205
00:12:06,052 --> 00:12:08,731
You said it you considered
her your family.

206
00:12:08,891 --> 00:12:10,052
And she raised you.

207
00:12:11,011 --> 00:12:12,611
Do you think I'll take such a risk

208
00:12:12,731 --> 00:12:13,692
by working with you?

209
00:12:14,172 --> 00:12:16,292
If a hunter teams up with a wolf cub,

210
00:12:16,332 --> 00:12:17,972
they could destroy the entire wolf den.

211
00:12:17,972 --> 00:12:19,131
Isn't that worth the gamble?

212
00:12:19,332 --> 00:12:20,771
Don't flatter yourself as a wolf.

213
00:12:21,212 --> 00:12:23,332
You could be the snake
in the farmer's story.

214
00:12:26,371 --> 00:12:26,851
Fine.

215
00:12:28,692 --> 00:12:31,131
I know you're not afraid
of snakes or wolves.

216
00:12:33,011 --> 00:12:34,572
But you're afraid of water.

217
00:12:36,092 --> 00:12:38,251
I also know your home address
and workplace.

218
00:12:38,412 --> 00:12:39,932
Even your artistic philosophy.

219
00:12:40,692 --> 00:12:41,972
Driving a car into water

220
00:12:42,611 --> 00:12:43,572
was me going too far.

221
00:12:44,092 --> 00:12:45,412
But I can't promise

222
00:12:45,412 --> 00:12:46,812
I won't do it again.

223
00:12:53,212 --> 00:12:55,011
You're truly something.

224
00:12:55,771 --> 00:12:57,651
How rare to hear you say something kind.

225
00:12:58,491 --> 00:12:59,412
What do you mean?

226
00:13:01,052 --> 00:13:02,891
After hearing your life story earlier,

227
00:13:03,212 --> 00:13:04,172
I genuinely felt

228
00:13:04,172 --> 00:13:05,851
a slight sense of empathy.

229
00:13:06,251 --> 00:13:07,172
I even forgot about

230
00:13:07,172 --> 00:13:08,251
our past unpleasantness.

231
00:13:09,011 --> 00:13:09,932
But just now

232
00:13:10,011 --> 00:13:11,212
your words

233
00:13:11,491 --> 00:13:13,531
revived my disgust toward you.

234
00:13:14,251 --> 00:13:15,412
You have a way with people.

235
00:13:16,771 --> 00:13:17,891
If that's the case,

236
00:13:18,092 --> 00:13:19,651
your being immune to all persuasion

237
00:13:19,651 --> 00:13:20,812
and your sarcastic skills

238
00:13:20,812 --> 00:13:21,972
are thoroughly impressive.

239
00:13:22,812 --> 00:13:24,092
A truly dedicated

240
00:13:24,092 --> 00:13:25,572
and virtuous artist.

241
00:13:29,972 --> 00:13:30,572
Come with me.

242
00:13:31,172 --> 00:13:31,851
To where?

243
00:13:32,851 --> 00:13:34,491
I'll show you a sculpture.

244
00:13:58,078 --> 00:14:02,332
(Temple of the Righteous Lord)

245
00:14:02,332 --> 00:14:03,452
In ancient times,

246
00:14:04,052 --> 00:14:07,131
a meteor fell
into South Mountain's ancient woods.

247
00:14:08,052 --> 00:14:09,371
The meteor melted into the earth,

248
00:14:09,611 --> 00:14:10,771
turning the soil turquoise.

249
00:14:11,692 --> 00:14:15,212
Plants and animals mutated,
and strange occurrences multiplied.

250
00:14:16,092 --> 00:14:19,611
Then a type of light-fearing,

251
00:14:20,572 --> 00:14:21,651
carnivorous savage beasts

252
00:14:21,651 --> 00:14:23,172
started roaming South Mountain.

253
00:14:24,371 --> 00:14:25,812
The locals

254
00:14:25,932 --> 00:14:27,812
named those beasts Earth Fiends.

255
00:14:28,371 --> 00:14:30,731
Earth Fiends were brutal killers.

256
00:14:30,812 --> 00:14:32,131
People suffered terribly.

257
00:14:33,332 --> 00:14:33,972
Later,

258
00:14:34,692 --> 00:14:36,172
the emperor sent troops

259
00:14:36,692 --> 00:14:38,491
to drive the Earth Fiends underground.

260
00:14:39,572 --> 00:14:41,172
The soldiers who stayed

261
00:14:41,812 --> 00:14:43,611
abandoned their identities

262
00:14:43,891 --> 00:14:45,692
and called themselves
South Mountain Hunters.

263
00:14:45,692 --> 00:14:47,292
and swore enmity with Earth Fiends.

264
00:14:47,452 --> 00:14:48,731
This legacy continues today.

265
00:14:51,812 --> 00:14:53,011
Such detailed settings?

266
00:14:53,212 --> 00:14:54,572
Not writing a novel wastes them.

267
00:14:54,692 --> 00:14:55,851
I've said my piece.

268
00:14:56,651 --> 00:14:57,731
Believe what you will.

269
00:14:59,611 --> 00:15:00,212
Go on.

270
00:15:01,251 --> 00:15:02,572
Those injured by Earth Fiends

271
00:15:02,932 --> 00:15:04,092
develop filmy tissue

272
00:15:04,371 --> 00:15:06,371
over wounds after some time,

273
00:15:06,812 --> 00:15:08,011
like rooting and sprouting.

274
00:15:08,771 --> 00:15:10,412
Though revealing this to an outsider

275
00:15:10,771 --> 00:15:11,651
breaks our rules,

276
00:15:12,172 --> 00:15:13,531
soon I'll also be an outsider.

277
00:15:13,531 --> 00:15:14,332
It doesn't matter.

278
00:15:15,572 --> 00:15:16,371
Besides,

279
00:15:17,131 --> 00:15:18,172
what I described earlier

280
00:15:18,172 --> 00:15:19,611
were beast-like Earth Fiends.

281
00:15:20,491 --> 00:15:22,651
Humanoid ones might differ entirely.

282
00:15:23,172 --> 00:15:24,011
So

283
00:15:24,692 --> 00:15:26,651
you're also a South Mountain Hunter,

284
