and I'll grant you one in return.

570
00:37:07,732 --> 00:37:08,651
I pay each time.

571
00:37:08,972 --> 00:37:09,972
Why so calculative?

572
00:37:10,091 --> 00:37:11,011
Because I don't want

573
00:37:11,011 --> 00:37:12,211
to get entangled with you.

574
00:37:12,691 --> 00:37:14,131
Fine, as you say.

575
00:37:14,372 --> 00:37:15,332
Have you decided?

576
00:37:16,571 --> 00:37:17,932
What's your request this time?

577
00:37:20,611 --> 00:37:21,372
I've decided.

578
00:37:21,772 --> 00:37:23,571
Add me on WeChat. Scan my code.

579
00:37:29,571 --> 00:37:31,051
What brings you here today?

580
00:37:32,171 --> 00:37:34,772
I tried a braised dish spot
last night and found it good.

581
00:37:35,091 --> 00:37:36,452
The owner said they do breakfast,

582
00:37:36,452 --> 00:37:38,651
so I woke early to get you some.

583
00:37:39,252 --> 00:37:39,972
Try it first.

584
00:37:40,171 --> 00:37:41,091
I haven't tried it.

585
00:37:41,372 --> 00:37:43,091
Don't expect too much.
It might disappoint.

586
00:37:46,292 --> 00:37:47,131
Not bad.

587
00:37:47,372 --> 00:37:48,131
It's good?

588
00:37:48,491 --> 00:37:49,452
I'll buy more next time.

589
00:37:54,531 --> 00:37:57,051
I saw the report.
Our business are thriving.

590
00:37:57,611 --> 00:37:58,892
Don't just see the surface.

591
00:37:59,051 --> 00:38:00,252
Such a large group

592
00:38:00,412 --> 00:38:03,292
has countless trivial matters
beneath your notice.

593
00:38:03,732 --> 00:38:05,011
Don't focus only on now either.

594
00:38:05,292 --> 00:38:07,211
The future remains uncertain.

595
00:38:08,051 --> 00:38:09,491
If Roadsound's competitors

596
00:38:09,611 --> 00:38:11,651
had half your crisis awareness,

597
00:38:11,772 --> 00:38:13,611
they wouldn't have stayed
underfoot forever.

598
00:38:15,091 --> 00:38:17,651
You think these internal
and external troubles are imaginary?

599
00:38:19,892 --> 00:38:21,091
That's why I brought breakfast

600
00:38:21,292 --> 00:38:22,332
to ease your mind.

601
00:38:25,412 --> 00:38:26,491
I heard the other day

602
00:38:27,171 --> 00:38:28,252
Xiong caught someone.

603
00:38:28,252 --> 00:38:29,011
What happened?

604
00:38:35,531 --> 00:38:37,892
I know you want to help me,

605
00:38:38,211 --> 00:38:39,892
but some grassroots matters

606
00:38:40,171 --> 00:38:41,772
are better left untouched.

607
00:38:41,852 --> 00:38:42,611
Understood.

608
00:38:46,491 --> 00:38:47,812
The schedule is tight today.

609
00:38:48,211 --> 00:38:50,452
I need to visit the farm
before heading to the office.

610
00:38:51,651 --> 00:38:53,332
You even personally
oversee the planting?

611
00:38:53,611 --> 00:38:55,452
I need to check. I can't rest easy.

612
00:39:24,091 --> 00:39:25,732
Anyone here?

613
00:39:46,611 --> 00:39:49,972
Speak up now if you want less suffering.

614
00:39:53,531 --> 00:39:54,812
I'm old.

615
00:39:55,412 --> 00:39:56,452
I can't handle turmoil.

616
00:39:56,772 --> 00:39:57,772
Let's talk civilly.

617
00:40:01,051 --> 00:40:02,852
Where's the base
of South Mountain Hunters?

618
00:40:03,131 --> 00:40:04,171
How many members in total?

619
00:40:04,892 --> 00:40:06,972
What's your next action plan?

620
00:40:08,292 --> 00:40:09,011
The base...

621
00:40:10,292 --> 00:40:12,292
The base is at the South Heavenly Gate.

622
00:40:13,211 --> 00:40:16,691
Their numbers are hundreds of thousands,
and they are from a celestial army.

623
00:40:17,372 --> 00:40:21,292
And they plan to descend
to eradicate demons and monsters.

624
00:40:26,211 --> 00:40:27,372
Bad with essay questions?

625
00:40:27,852 --> 00:40:29,332
Then we'll make it multiple choice.

626
00:40:30,651 --> 00:40:31,732
How do you want to die?

627
00:40:32,412 --> 00:40:34,332
Bleed out? Heart extraction?

628
00:40:34,651 --> 00:40:36,011
Or live burial?

629
00:40:36,372 --> 00:40:38,812
If you'd brought Mrs. Hua with you,

630
00:40:39,412 --> 00:40:41,051
I'd choose live burial.

631
00:40:42,211 --> 00:40:44,131
We couldn't be together in life.

632
00:40:44,531 --> 00:40:45,932
Sharing a grave in death

633
00:40:46,051 --> 00:40:48,091
would fulfill my wish.

634
00:40:48,332 --> 00:40:49,972
That woman in the hospital

635
00:40:50,651 --> 00:40:51,611
is in such bad shape.

636
00:40:52,772 --> 00:40:54,892
She'll never speak again.

637
00:41:08,211 --> 00:41:09,531
He's quite spirited.

638
00:41:11,171 --> 00:41:12,252
Calm him down.

639
00:41:23,852 --> 00:41:24,812
Long time no see.

640
00:41:24,892 --> 00:41:26,211
Who are you?

641
00:41:27,372 --> 00:41:28,491
Twenty years ago,

642
00:41:28,932 --> 00:41:29,772
I offended you.

643
00:41:30,932 --> 00:41:31,732
Who?

644
00:41:34,611 --> 00:41:36,372
Don't tell me you're holding a grudge,

645
00:41:37,732 --> 00:41:39,732
wanting me to repay you with a leg?

646
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:59,343
(Greenhouse)

647
00:42:10,372 --> 00:42:12,292
Don't be fooled
by his usual carefree demeanor.

648
00:42:12,812 --> 00:42:14,772
He definitely has his own thoughts.

649
00:42:15,171 --> 00:42:16,491
He just buries them well.

650
00:42:17,491 --> 00:42:19,051
It's fine if it's not a deal-breaker.

651
00:42:19,651 --> 00:42:21,011
It's been many years.

652
00:42:21,772 --> 00:42:23,531
This whole mother-and-son-bond act

653
00:42:24,011 --> 00:42:26,091
has to continue, doesn't it?

654
00:42:26,412 --> 00:42:27,531
No matter what,

655
00:42:27,972 --> 00:42:29,892
Yan Tuo is my own son.

656
00:42:31,412 --> 00:42:33,892
Wake the old man below
and resume interrogation.

657
00:42:34,452 --> 00:42:36,452
We must extract information
about the Mad Blade.

658
00:42:36,611 --> 00:42:37,772
Understood. We'll handle it.

659
00:42:58,812 --> 00:42:59,651
(Lin Ling?)

660
00:43:02,011 --> 00:43:02,732
(Lin Ling?)

661
00:43:04,732 --> 00:43:06,171
(Where are you? Come out.)

662
00:43:07,531 --> 00:43:08,332
(Lin Ling.)

663
00:43:10,091 --> 00:43:10,892
(Lin Ling?)

664
00:43:12,972 --> 00:43:14,171
(Come out now.)

665
00:43:14,892 --> 00:43:15,852
(This is not fun.)

666
00:43:15,932 --> 00:43:17,611
(Ms. Lin will scold us
if she finds out.)

667
00:43:20,252 --> 00:43:21,011
(Lin Ling?)

668
00:43:21,691 --> 00:43:22,452
(Lin Ling?)

669
00:43:25,292 --> 00:43:25,972
(Lin Ling?)

670
00:43:53,976 --> 00:43:56,664
(Toxic and Hazardous)

671
00:44:24,312 --> 00:44:25,200
Lin Xirou.

672
00:44:28,560 --> 00:44:30,880
This humanoid Earth Fiend
and the Roadsound Group

673
00:44:30,920 --> 00:44:32,280
must be closely connected.

674
00:44:32,600 --> 00:44:34,080
This intel is crucial.

675
00:44:34,160 --> 00:44:35,600
We'll investigate immediately.

676
00:44:36,160 --> 00:44:36,800
Thank you.

677
00:44:37,600 --> 00:44:38,640
How's Sun Zhou?

678
00:44:40,440 --> 00:44:41,880
Overcast skies may make us

679
00:44:42,760 --> 00:44:43,720
miss the window.

680
00:44:44,200 --> 00:44:45,120
Do what you can.

681
00:44:45,320 --> 00:44:47,560
If even heaven won't save him,

682
00:44:47,920 --> 00:44:48,880
we can't help with that.

683
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:50,200
Then

684
00:44:50,520 --> 00:44:52,840
we'll have to banish him to Golden Gate

685
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:54,160
by Hunters' rules.

686
00:44:55,240 --> 00:44:56,680
Those wounded by Earth Fiends before

687
00:44:56,760 --> 00:44:58,800
and became infected
without timely fire purification

688
00:44:58,880 --> 00:45:00,120
were all Hunters

689
00:45:00,560 --> 00:45:02,040
who vowed to accept this fate.

690
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:03,240
They were all prepared.

691
00:45:03,560 --> 00:45:05,080
But Sun Zhou is a civilian.

692
00:45:07,640 --> 00:45:08,840
For him,

693
00:45:09,720 --> 00:45:10,800
it's too cruel.

694
00:45:10,808 --> 00:45:11,465
Of course.

695
00:45:12,240 --> 00:45:13,880
I'll explore alternatives.

696
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:20,600
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

697
00:45:23,880 --> 00:45:24,800
Are you still there?

698
00:45:25,528 --> 00:45:25,968
Yes.

699
00:45:26,720 --> 00:45:27,680
Speaking of which,

700
00:45:28,400 --> 00:45:30,800
about the informant you mentioned,
who tipped you off

701
00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:32,840
about Lin Xirou and the Roadsound Group,

702
00:45:33,048 --> 00:45:34,090
who is he?

703
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:35,720
You think he's unreliable?

704
00:45:35,840 --> 00:45:37,520
I'm worried for your safety.

705
00:45:37,720 --> 00:45:39,120
How did you connect with him?

706
00:45:41,240 --> 00:45:42,720
Maybe my unique constitution

707
00:45:42,920 --> 00:45:45,000
attracts oddities.

708
00:45:46,640 --> 00:45:48,520
We've got plenty of oddities here too.

709
00:45:49,360 --> 00:45:52,320
They're all here at the hospital
keeping watch over Mrs. Hua.

710
00:45:52,880 --> 00:45:55,160
I gotta go. It's starting up again.

711
00:45:55,768 --> 00:45:56,284
Okay.

712
00:46:00,904 --> 00:46:05,264
♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

713
00:46:05,264 --> 00:46:09,584
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

714
00:46:09,584 --> 00:46:14,024
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

715
00:46:14,024 --> 00:46:16,464
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

716
00:46:16,464 --> 00:46:20,544
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

717
00:46:20,544 --> 00:46:24,904
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

718
00:46:24,904 --> 00:46:29,264
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

719
00:46:29,264 --> 00:46:33,624
♪If we don't retreat,
we'll go through it together♪

720
00:46:33,624 --> 00:46:37,984
♪Heaven-kindled flames are different♪

721
00:46:37,984 --> 00:46:42,264
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

722
00:46:42,264 --> 00:46:46,824
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

723
00:46:46,824 --> 00:46:54,544
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪

